> 4 The words “Chairperson of the” omitted by the Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of India (Registration and Operations of Branch Offices of Foreign Reinsurers other than Lloyd’s) (First Amendment) Regulations, 2016 dated 28<sup>th</sup> January, 2016 (w.e.f. 04th February 2016); 

> 5 The words “Chairperson of the” omitted by the Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of India (Registration and Operations of Branch Offices of Foreign Reinsurers other than Lloyd’s) (First Amendment) Regulations, 2016 dated 28<sup>th</sup> January, 2016 (w.e.f. 04th February 2016); 

